21:07.360 --> 21:08.520
[Steve chuckling]

21:09.240 --> 21:11.120
You got it, birthday boy.

21:11.160 --> 21:14.280
And so it all hinges

21:11.160 --> 21:14.280
on the last night.

21:19.320 --> 21:21.040
<i>I'd used up all my goes</i>

21:21.080 --> 21:23.520
<i>and now Mr. Zee needed</i>

21:21.080 --> 21:23.520
<i>a final answer.</i>

21:25.040 --> 21:28.200
<i>Guess correctly and I'd join</i>

21:25.040 --> 21:28.200
<i>the family business.</i>

21:28.240 --> 21:33.400
<i>Guess wrong</i>

21:28.240 --> 21:33.400
<i>and I'd have to make</i>

21:28.240 --> 21:33.400
<i>my way in life with no head.</i>

