<i>I had no clue what to say</i>

21:33.440 --> 21:36.840
<i>and I racked my brain</i>

21:33.440 --> 21:36.840
<i>for inspiration.</i>

21:38.560 --> 21:40.480
<i>What could cause</i>

21:38.560 --> 21:40.480
<i>a scar like that?</i>

