<i>I'd heard him say he'd</i>

21:44.320 --> 21:46.720
<i>grown up by the sea</i>

21:46.760 --> 21:49.280
<i>and that he'd often go</i>

21:46.760 --> 21:49.280
<i>swimming there.</i>

21:56.280 --> 21:58.200
You answer, now!

22:01.720 --> 22:06.080
<i>She mouthed the words</i>

22:01.720 --> 22:06.080
<i>"Stin Ree," which I think</i>

22:01.720 --> 22:06.080
<i>means good luck.</i>

22:13.520 --> 22:16.040
All right! I am ready

22:13.520 --> 22:16.040
to give my answer.

22:17.280 --> 22:20.080
It has something

22:17.280 --> 22:20.080
to do with the ocean.

22:21.600 --> 22:23.360
Something very dangerous.

22:25.760 --> 22:29.240
You got your scar...

22:32.200 --> 22:33.640
water skiing!

22:35.200 --> 22:36.360
Yeah...

22:38.600 --> 22:40.400
[laughing]

22:40.440 --> 22:42.880
