22:40.440 --> 22:42.880
He's an idiot, but I like him.

22:44.680 --> 22:48.040
<i>I'd guessed correctly.</i>

22:44.680 --> 22:48.040
<i>And Mr. Zee was as good</i>

22:44.680 --> 22:48.040
<i>as his word.</i>

22:48.080 --> 22:52.280
<i>The next day, I was officially</i>

22:48.080 --> 22:52.280
<i>welcomed into the family</i>

22:48.080 --> 22:52.280
<i>and made a delivery boy.</i>

22:53.320 --> 22:55.160
[laughing]

22:56.680 --> 22:59.440
So, I learned

22:56.680 --> 22:59.440
a valuable lesson that day.

22:59.480 --> 23:02.280
In fact, I learned 12 of them

22:59.480 --> 23:02.280
which I will now explain.

23:02.320 --> 23:03.160
First lesson--

23:03.200 --> 23:05.400
No. Enough is enough.

23:05.440 --> 23:06.560
Steve, ask the question.

