23:11.280 --> 23:14.240
Get this wrong and

23:11.280 --> 23:14.240
the Lichfield

23:11.280 --> 23:14.240
mixed martial arts center

23:14.280 --> 23:17.400
gets a 6 foot 8

23:14.280 --> 23:17.400
white belt with

23:14.280 --> 23:17.400
